### Data Management Patterns

### Cache-First Architecture
The dashboard follows a strict cache-first pattern:
- **Dashboard Open**: Check cache ‚Üí if miss, make API call ‚Üí save to cache
- **Page Navigation**: Use cached data only (no API calls)
- **Refresh Button**: Clear cache ‚Üí force fresh API calls ‚Üí update cache
- **Account/Date Change**: New cache key ‚Üí check cache ‚Üí fallback to API

